00:29:25.263 --> 00:29:26.473 line:85.83%,end
Damn it!

00:29:36.900 --> 00:29:39.986 line:85.83%,end
Yes, I'm uneducated and poor.

00:29:40.487 --> 00:29:42.238 line:85.83%,end
