00:30:04.594 --> 00:30:08.306 line:85.83%,end
Do you have any idea
what kind of man Kim Man-dong is?

00:30:17.023 --> 00:30:19.359 line:85.83%,end
You communist bastard!

00:30:24.197 --> 00:30:26.449 line:85.83%,end
